---
title: Easy Chorizo, Potato & Veggie Traybake with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Feta
description: Baking veggies on a tray in the oven, there’s no fuss and a tonne of flavour all come together. The chorizo is an addition that we
are absolutely sure will knock your socks off!
